Descriptions


kz_city_extreme
Original map by fact or fiction
contains 1 course: city_extreme
notes: the map is one giant model, which may cause some lag

kz_small_facility
Original map by Chrizzy
contains 3 courses: kz_small_facility 1, kz_small_facility 2 and kz_boxes

kz_strafe_protraining
Original map by SoUlFaThEr
contains 3 courses: kz_arches, strafe_ez and strafe_hard

kz_tombraider
Original map by SoUlFaThEr
contains 2 courses: kz_tombraider and kz_egyptian_pillars
notes: this map is non-linear and can be confusing, I wrote a simple guide to help with this. http://5.199.136.88/tombraider
notes for server owners: set shavit_misc_startonspawn to 0

kz_utopia
Original map by fact or fiction
contains 2 courses: kz_utopia and mini bhop

kz_wallclimb
Original map by Solid
contains 2 courses: kz_wallclimb and kz_angle_climber
